{"type":null,"faqId":32792,"title":"为什么有的时候闪光灯拍出照片会蒙成一片？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">发生这种问题的时候有可能：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1、是因为您的手放在了闪光灯的附近，手指作为一个反射面会反摄一定的光，会造成相机的画面对比度不好。移开手指后再拍摄照片画面不蒙了，就说明是这个问题造成的。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2、有可能您使用的手机壳在闪光灯的附近，形成一个较大的光的反射面造成，摘掉手机壳，画面就正常了，说明是这个原因。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7494","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748408000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":4,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"散光灯,拍照,照片,模糊","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}